2	 * LayerInfinite MCP Server — rest-client.ts
3	 * ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
4	 * V2: LiApiClient (LI REST API) + UpstreamMCPClient (MCP JSON-RPC proxy).
5	 *
6	 * LiApiClient replaces V1 RestClient — fetches scores, policy decisions,
7	 * and logs outcomes to the LayerInfinite REST API.
